text: Tancheng may refer to the following places in China: *Tancheng County (郯城县), Shandong *Tancheng, Anhui (坛城镇), town in Mengcheng County *Tancheng Subdistrict (潭城街道), Jianyang, Fujian *Tancheng, Pingtan County (潭城镇), Fuzhou, Fujian *Tancheng, Shandong (郯城镇), town in and seat of Tancheng County
title: Tancheng
